name: Around-pune
tagline: Application Created for Android Code Labs in Pune GDG
body:
### Welcome to Around Pune
This is a sample application created for seminar in Pune Google Developer Group. For Newcomers this will be basic start up app to see how to integrate real time Rest API to android application.

check out PPT as well which will give you some idea about sample project.
